        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Hold TION tiles together:</span> When you see T+I+O+N on your rack, treat them as a unit. You only need 3-4 more tiles to complete a bingo. Scan for Q+U+E+S (QUESTION), F+R+A+C (FRACTION), or P+O+S+I (POSITION).</p></div>
