        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Pair with premium squares:</span> 8-letter -TION words often reach triple-word scores. QUESTION through a TWS = 51 base + 50 bonus = 101 points in one turn. Position your play to maximize letter multipliers on Q or F.</p></div>
